{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Team, we've got a new survey ready to go out to customers. Can we review the questions in our next meeting?", "created_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "product_customization", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Reminder: We're having a session on the latest electric vehicle technology trends tomorrow. Please make sure to attend.", "created_at": 1620501000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "I've noticed a trend in the feedback: customers appreciate our focus on sustainability. It's something we should continue to highlight in our marketing.", "created_at": 1620502000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "product_customization", "user": "john_doe", "message": "I've updated the Q2 project plan. Please review and let me know if you have any questions.", "created_at": 1620503000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Thanks, Emily. Yes, sustainability should continue to be a key message in our marketing strategy.", "created_at": 1620504000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "product_customization", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "Just a reminder, we have a meeting with the compliance team next week to discuss the latest cross-border regulations.", "created_at": 1620505000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Anyone attending the electric vehicles expo next month? It would be a great opportunity to network and learn more about the latest industry trends.", "created_at": 1620506000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "Based on our most recent customer preference surveys, there's a significant interest in more earthy color finishes for our mid-range vehicle line. I'm considering proposing this to the product team. Thoughts?", "create_at": 1620500000000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "sales_marketing", "channel": "customer_feedback", "user": "jane_smith", "message": "Sounds like a solid strategy, Emily. The market seems to be leaning towards more natural, earthy tones lately. Plus, it'll give our customers more customization options.", "create_at": 1620500001000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "product_customization", "user": "emily_lee", "message": "Based on the feedback from customers, there's a clear demand for earthy color finishes for our mid-range vehicles. I recommend we consider this for future customization options.", "create_at": 1620500002000}}
{"type": "post", "post": {"team": "product_development", "channel": "product_customization", "user": "john_doe", "message": "Good insight, Emily. Let's take this into consideration in our next product development meeting. The market trends seem to align with this feedback.", "create_at": 1620500003000}}
